The supplemental lighting system shines in a field of dragon fruit plants on the outskirts of Nanning, capital of South China's Guangxi Zhuang Autonomous Region on Sunday. The advanced system can catalyze the 2,000 mu of plants to flower and bear fruit in winter. Photo: IC 
